{"tid":451543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"High爆即興演出 Tanya孖AY大跳《無心睡眠》","createTime":"2017-10-29T10:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T01:18:26.000Z","uid":156068,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3cc6f3846e943372eac326eeed9aaeefffac58ac","tid":451543,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T10:27:40.000Z","msg":"同朋友開餐，除咗食好西仲想食埋氣氛？北角渣華道熟食中心大牌檔東寶小館肯定上榜，去過朋友嘅朋友都會樂而忘返，皆因嗰度開飯會播歌都似搞埋嘉年華。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員陳淑莊(Tanya)係東寶鐵粉，經常喺嗰度打躉，上周五佢同朋友又去捧場，咁啱公民黨黨魁楊岳橋（AY）就喺另一枱。據知當晚另有一位歌星在場，令到現場氣氛更高漲，唔少人企起身腳印印。<br />\n可能已經warm up咗，Tanya同AY一聽到《無心睡眠》，更情不自禁自動埋位合跳，「WHOO-OH-O 無心睡眠，WHOO-OH-O 腦交戰」，哥哥嘅經典舞姿又重現，兩人舞姿好合拍，帶領全場high爆。<br />\nTanya噚日喺Facebook上載同AY跳舞嘅短片，立即喺網絡瘋傳，可能因為跳得有默契，有人質疑唔通早有演出預謀？當晚踩住3吋半高踭鞋嘅Tanya同八方講純粹即興，「完全無排過，雖然好齊，哈哈哈......」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/182704_5110890abf702f31882a34fde0d8dc01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F182704_5110890abf702f31882a34fde0d8dc01.jpg&h=73596f26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/182734_0568ab2dd1ad3d6aecf07b9aabb57d8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F182734_0568ab2dd1ad3d6aecf07b9aabb57d8e.jpg&h=f074ff86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33e97e9220945daad3c7726735d7c43382b7b3d0","tid":451543,"uid":156068,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/205508_9dd2f6a32d7d1ee96cc9b31d47e02ca6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F205508_9dd2f6a32d7d1ee96cc9b31d47e02ca6.jpg&h=a17a3374&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2acafc1561360b4bfd99914d577b8370313fbc4","tid":451543,"uid":141078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:57:35.000Z","msg"